{"id":611011,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/05/【图说天朝】真是完整的作品/","date":"2019-05-23T09:04:34Z","modified":"2019-05-23T09:04:34Z","title":"【图说天朝】真是完整的作品","content":"<p>5月23日，有新浪微博网友热传一副名为“言论自由”的展览作，黑框的作品中仅有一行字“根据相关法律法规和政策，该作品已被删除”，该作品身处一堆精美画作之中似乎显得有些单薄和格格不入。然而有网友将其拍照发布于新浪微博之后，最终遭到官方删除。有网友对此评论称“这样才是完整的作品”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-611013\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/006QWjcHly1g3bbtoasdjj30u00u00vy.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/006QWjcHly1g3bbtoasdjj30u00u00vy.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/006QWjcHly1g3bbtoasdjj30u00u00vy-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/006QWjcHly1g3bbtoasdjj30u00u00vy-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/006QWjcHly1g3bbtoasdjj30u00u00vy-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/006QWjcHly1g3bbtoasdjj30u00u00vy-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-611014\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D7LCTgkUcAICF4y.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D7LCTgkUcAICF4y.png 646w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D7LCTgkUcAICF4y-266x300.png 266w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-611015\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D7NSSdIXsAEgh82.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D7NSSdIXsAEgh82.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D7NSSdIXsAEgh82-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D7NSSdIXsAEgh82-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-611016\" src=\"https://chinad